Data.TextValue: SELECT p.[personid] ,p.[salarynumber] ,p.[firstname] ,p.[prefix] ,p.[name] ,d.[name] as department ,p.[freetext1] as title FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_persons] p LEFT JOIN [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_departments] d ON d.department_id = p.departmentid
SELECT [personid] ,[salarynumber] ,[firstname] ,[prefix] ,[name] ,[departmentid] ,[freetext1] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_persons] WHERE salarynumber = '%pers_nr%'

SELECT p.[personid] AS 'PersonID' ,p.[salarynumber] AS 'Administratienummer' ,p.[firstname] AS 'Voornaam' ,p.[prefix] AS 'Tussenvoegsel' ,p.[name] AS 'Naam' ,ak.accesskeyid AS 'Pas accessKeyID' ,ak.rcn AS 'Pas RCN' ,CASE ak.valid WHEN 1 THEN 'Bruikbaar' WHEN 0 THEN 'Niet bruikbaar' ELSE 'Onbekend' END AS 'Geldigheid' FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_persons] p LEFT JOIN _iProtect_accessKeys ak ON ak.personid = p.personid WHERE p.salarynumber = '%AD_employeeNumber%'

SELECT p.[personid] AS 'PersonID' ,p.[salarynumber] AS 'Administratienummer' ,p.[firstname] AS 'Voornaam' ,p.[prefix] AS 'Tussenvoegsel' ,p.[name] AS 'Naam' ,ak.accesskeyid AS 'Pas accessKeyID' ,ak.rcn AS 'Pas RCN' ,CASE ak.valid WHEN 1 THEN 'Bruikbaar' WHEN 0 THEN 'Niet bruikbaar' ELSE 'Onbekend' END AS 'Geldigheid' ,r.keygroupname AS 'Keygroup' ,r.readername AS 'Reader'
FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_persons] p LEFT JOIN _iProtect_accessKeys ak ON ak.personid = p.personid LEFT JOIN _iProtect_accesskeys_linked_to_keygroups akkg ON akkg.accesskeyid = ak.accesskeyid LEFT JOIN _iProtect_readers_and_readergroups r ON r.keygroupid = akkg.keygroupid WHERE p.salarynumber = '%AD_employeeNumber%'

SELECT [rcn] ,[personid] ,[cardclassid] ,[valid] ,[unlimited] ,[startdate] ,[enddate] ,[expirationdate] ,[keyuseid] ,[blockclass] ,[lasttranstime] ,[areanr] ,[areanrtime] ,[parkareanr] ,[parkareanrtime] ,[accesskeyid] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_accessKeys]

SELECT [rcn] ,[personid] ,[cardclassid] ,[valid] ,[unlimited] ,[startdate] ,[enddate] ,[expirationdate] ,[keyuseid] ,[blockclass] ,[lasttranstime] ,[areanr] ,[areanrtime] ,[parkareanr] ,[parkareanrtime] ,[accesskeyid] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_accessKeys] WHERE personid = '%iProtect_person_id%'

SELECT p.personid ,p.salarynumber ,ak.accesskeyid ,ak.rcn ,akkg.keykeygroupid ,kg.keygroupid ,kg.name FROM _iProtect_persons p LEFT JOIN _iProtect_accessKeys ak ON ak.personid = p.personid LEFT JOIN _iProtect_accesskeys_linked_to_keygroups akkg ON akkg.accesskeyid = ak.accesskeyid LEFT JOIN _iProtect_keygroups kg ON kg.keygroupid = akkg.keygroupid WHERE p.salarynumber = '%pers_nr%' AND ak.valid = 1
SELECT [keygroupid] ,[name] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_iProtect_keygroups]

SELECT employee.[pers_nr] ,employee.[straat] ,employee.[huisnummer] ,employee.[huisnummer_tv] ,employee.[postcode] ,employee.[woonplaats] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_profit_employees] employee LEFT JOIN _profit_employee_placements_time placements_time ON placements_time.pers_nr = employee.pers_nr
WHERE placements_time.formatie_percentage IS NOT NULL AND placements_time.formatie_percentage != 0 AND placements_time.einddatum >= getdate() AND placements_time.einddatum_contract >= getdate() AND placements_time.begindatum <= getdate() AND placements_time.begindatum_contract <= getdate()
ORDER BY employee.pers_nr ASC ,placements_time.einddatum_contract DESC ,placements_time.einddatum DESC ,placements_time.rooster_uren_pw DESC ,placements_time.formatie_percentage DESC

SELECT employee.[pers_nr] ,employee.[roepnaam] ,employee.[voorletters] ,employee.[voornaam] ,employee.[e_vrvg] ,employee.[e_naam] ,employee.[p_vrvg] ,employee.[p_naam] ,employee.[gbrk_nm] ,employee.[geslacht] ,employee.[tel_werk] ,placements_time.[functie_oms] ,placements_time.[kostenplaats_code] ,Emanager.[pers_nr] as mngr_pers_nr ,employee.[pers_nr]
FROM _profit_employees employee LEFT JOIN _profit_employee_placements_time placements_time ON placements_time.pers_nr = employee.pers_nr LEFT JOIN _profit_managers managers ON managers.oe_code = placements_time.oe_code LEFT JOIN _profit_employees Emanager ON Emanager.pers_nr = managers.oe_manager_pers_nr
WHERE placements_time.formatie_percentage IS NOT NULL AND placements_time.formatie_percentage != 0
AND placements_time.einddatum >= getdate() AND placements_time.einddatum_contract >= getdate()
ORDER BY employee.pers_nr ASC ,placements_time.einddatum_contract DESC ,placements_time.einddatum DESC ,placements_time.rooster_uren_pw DESC ,placements_time.formatie_percentage DESC
SELECT employee.[pers_nr] FROM _profit_employees employee

,placements_time.[einddatum_contract]

SELECT [oe_code] ,[oe_manager_pers_nr] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_profit_managers]
SELECT DISTINCT kostenplaats_code ,kostenplaats_oms FROM _profit_employee_placements_time
SELECT DISTINCT kostenplaats_oms ,kostenplaats_code FROM _temp_allowed_roles_modification_kostenplaatsen

SELECT DISTINCT [oe_code] ,[oe_oms] ,[oe_code] as kol1 ,[oe_code] as kol2 ,'%tag_keywords_prefix_afd%' + [oe_code] AS keywords ,[oe_oms] AS description FROM _profit_employee_placements_time ORDER BY keywords ASC

SELECT DISTINCT [oe_code] ,[oe_oms] ,functie_code ,[functie_oms] ,'%tag_keywords_prefix_afd%' + [oe_code] + ';%tag_keywords_prefix_func%' + functie_code AS keywords ,[oe_oms] + ' - ' + [functie_oms] AS description
FROM _profit_employee_placements_time ORDER BY keywords ASC

SELECT DISTINCT [functie_code] ,[functie_oms] ,[functie_code] as kol1 ,[functie_code] as kol2 ,'%tag_keywords_prefix_func%' + [functie_code] AS keywords ,[functie_oms] AS description FROM _profit_employee_placements_time ORDER BY keywords ASC
SELECT [Code] ,[Telefoonnr] FROM [ASZUltimo_prod].[dba].[_applview_PhoneBook] WHERE [Code] = '%pers_nr%'

SELECT t1.pnr AS 'Personeelsnummer' ,t1.winaccount AS 'sAMACcountName' ,t1.[attribuutsoort] AS 'Soort' ,t1.[nummer] AS 'Nummer' ,t1.[datumuitgifte] AS 'Datum Uitgifte' ,CONVERT(varchar,t1.[datumuitgifte],105) AS 'Datum Uitgifte NL' ,t1.[datumretour] AS 'Datum Retour' ,CONVERT(varchar,t1.[datumretour],105) AS 'Datum Retour NL' ,t1.[datumverlies] AS 'Datum Verlies' ,CONVERT(varchar,t1.[datumverlies],105) AS 'Datum Verlies NL' ,CASE t1.[2=actief/8=vermist] WHEN 2 THEN 'Actief' WHEN 8 THEN 'Vermist' ELSE 'Onbekend' END AS 'status' FROM ULTIMOLOGIN.UMRA_DA t1 WHERE t1.pnr ='%pers_nr%' ORDER BY pnr ASC, t1.[datumuitgifte] ASC, t1.[attribuutsoort] ASC
SELECT [pers_nr] ,[samaccountname] ,[van] ,[tot] FROM [UMRA].[dbo].[_samaccountname_history]

SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR, p.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', REPLACE(p.naam_samen + ', ' + p.e_roepnaam + ' ' + ISNULL(p.vrvg_samen,''),' ','') as 'vol_nm', p.e_vrlt, p.e_roepnaam, p.vrvg_samen, p.naam_samen, f.func_kd, f.func_oms, a.OE_KORT_NM, a.OE_VOL_NM, c.indnst_dt, c.uitdnst_dt FROM dpib010 p INNER JOIN dpic300 c ON c.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpib023 a ON a.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpic351 f on f.func_kd = c.primfunc_kd ORDER BY p.pers_nr

SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR, p.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', REPLACE(p.naam_samen + ', ' + p.e_roepnaam + ' ' + ISNULL(p.vrvg_samen,''),' ','') as 'vol_nm', p.e_vrlt, p.e_roepnaam, p.vrvg_samen, p.naam_samen, f.func_oms, a.OE_VOL_NM, c.indnst_dt, c.uitdnst_dt FROM dpib010 p INNER JOIN dpic300 c ON c.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpib023 a ON a.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpic351 f on f.func_kd = c.primfunc_kd WHERE c.uitdnst_dt > GETDATE() ORDER BY c.indnst_dt

SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR, p.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', REPLACE(p.naam_samen + ', ' + p.e_roepnaam + ' ' + ISNULL(p.vrvg_samen,''),' ','') as 'vol_nm', p.e_vrlt, p.e_roepnaam, p.vrvg_samen, p.naam_samen, f.func_oms, a.OE_VOL_NM, c.indnst_dt, c.uitdnst_dt FROM dpib010 p INNER JOIN dpic300 c ON c.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpib023 a ON a.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpic351 f on f.func_kd = c.primfunc_kd WHERE c.uitdnst_dt < GETDATE() ORDER BY p.pers_nr

SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR, p.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', p.e_vrlt, p.e_roepnaam, p.vrvg_samen, p.naam_samen, func_oms, oe_vol_nm, indnst_dt, uitdnst_dt FROM dpib010 p INNER JOIN dpic300 c ON c.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpib023 a ON a.pers_nr = p.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpic351 f ON c.primfunc_kd = f.func_kd WHERE p.pers_nr = %employeeID%
